author: MIT OpenCourseWare
description:
MIT OpenCourseWare, the Massachusetts OER Advisory Council, and Open Education Global announce that they will co-host the 2026 OE Global Conference in Cambridge, Massachusetts, from September 30 to October 2.
 
Speakers: Shiba Nemat-Nasser, Sharon Lin, Yvonne Ng, Robert J. Awkward, Amy Brand, Chris Bourg, Michel Anne-Frederic DeGraff, Hal Abelson, Sally Kornbluth, Gil Strang
 
License: Creative Commons BY-NC-SA
More information at https://ocw.mit.edu/terms
More courses at https://ocw.mit.edu

title: 2026 OE Global Conference Save the Date Announcement
